f with a simple wipe. I honestly couldn\u2019t own fabric chairs or couches without it. \ud83e\udd23\n\n4. Steam cleaner \u2013 my favourite for deep cleaning the kitchen. It melts away grease and grime, saving so much time. No scrubbing needed\u2026 just steam & wipe!\n\n5. Damp duster \u2013 perfect for grabbing dust instead of spreading it around. I love using it on skirting boards, blinds, shutters and other dusty surfaces.\n\n6. Wet & dry vacuum \u2013 a total game changer. Being able to vacuum and mop at the same time saves so much time. No more dragging around a traditional mop and bucket!\n\n#amazonfinds @amazonaustralia", "timestamp": "2026-07-07T02:53:05.000Z", "videoDuration": 34.433, "videoPlayCount": 336464, "videoViewCount": 58784, "likesCount": 1903, "commentsCount": 651, "displayUrl": "https://scontent-mia3-2.cdninstagram.com/v/t51.82787-15/740779879_18095982299369719_7342140402824859869_n.jpg?stp=dst-jpg_e15_tt6&_nc_ht=scontent-mia3-2.cdninstagram.com&_nc_cat=107&_nc_oc=Q6cZ2gFCV8orZcufGJQ-tTD-4o8eNnqv6MBU6BEzMb06k-XPm8KIB8hdY-1XFSNsxl20VWA&_nc_ohc=jRlzyDA_YUQQ7kNvwH-2E7Z&_nc_gid=-e5i67rULTmRMw8DxqbEcA&edm=ADp7STQBAAAA&ccb=7-5&oh=00_AQAOSSALg5AoHCTILamigEvqWD0AvTPWqr5TMp_YvEWJlw&oe=6A61BCB4&_nc_sid=c6f216", "videoUrl": "https://scontent-mia3-2.cdninstagram.com/o1/v/t2/f2/m86/AQP99vHU1cXXjfQevQpIhyT1XyrGcBPbzUrktxpx5NieI-lvlRO-VecMSgyKqGy18mtV2-ZjsQoORHuZ4tQAg7mnidjjJivXgBZwft0.mp4?_nc_cat=105&_nc_sid=5e9851&_nc_ht=scontent-mia3-2.cdninstagram.com&_nc_ohc=ne_dtyNSto8Q7kNvwFSneZD&efg=eyJ2ZW5jb2RlX3RhZyI6Inhwdl9wcm9ncmVzc2l2ZS5JTlNUQUdSQU0uQUQuQzMuNzIwLmRhc2hfYmFzZWxpbmVfMV92MSIsInhwdl9hc3NldF9pZCI6Mjc0MjExMTE1Nzc0OTk3NjksImFzc2V0X2FnZV9kYXlzIjoxMSwidmlfdXNlY2FzZV9pZCI6MTIzNzQsImR1cmF0aW9uX3MiOjM0LCJ1cmxnZW5fc291cmNlIjoid3d3In0%3D&ccb=17-1&vs=ffcf9ee74ecc3d56&_nc_&_nc_gid=GM1p1zq5W44uNsNcdzJ4wg&_nc_ss=72a8c&_nc_zt=28&oh=00_AQD3veDBlpTTNc11IipC-LSos1doAEi7xWAz_3d5bi4Kfw&oe=6A5DD362", "musicInfo": {"artist_name": "Instagram", "song_name": "Mouse click (s